Package: lintr
Title: How stylish is your code?
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Jim Hester <james.f.hester@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
URL: https://github.com/jimhester/lintr
BugReports: https://github.com/jimhester/lintr/issues
